name: CyberStars #1 (Aldhafera)
description:
In the CyberStars series, twenty-four comets are thrown to the ground, each of which is a lucky star and is responsible for fulfilling a special wish from its owner. Each star has its own name, which is the name of a star in the Old Testament and contains a thousand secrets.  How much of an unfulfilled wish do you have? The last star is the most perfect of them and this is the great and most special desire. This star is very rare and valuable. Generative 
CyberStars #1 (Aldhafera)
